2001-07-22 Sunday 11:23  twm

	* smapi.pas (1.2, smapi-2_2_3-release, smapi-2_2_2-release,
	smapi-2_2_1-release): As of now I will stop maintaining smapi.pas.
	It turned out that because of the alignment of the structures
	passed between sampi and calling programs is left to the compiler,
	it is likely to need constant rechecking whether the fields are
	still in sync. I am not going to do that.  So this is the last
	update I will post.

2001-07-09 Monday 20:52  joerg.jaspert

